D2->S1:Here's the signed quote
note over D2

    **put /quotes/382987a8-75ce-4037-b500-c475e08c1727**

    {
        "transferAmount": {
            "currency": "MWS"
            , "amount": "5000"
        }
        , "payeeReceiveAmount": {
            "currency": "ZMW"
            , "amount": "95"
        },
        "payeeFspFee": {
